      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from certified coupon tests on same lot material; geometric dimensions from CMM measurements of actual test specimens.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus and yield strength were obtained from ASTM E8 tensile tests on coupons from the same material lot as the test constructs. CMM measurements of screw OD, rod diameter, and setscrew torque were used to populate the FEA geometry. Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (N=500) to bound QoI variability."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
