      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison using E/uval metric; acceptance threshold E/uval < 1.96 and QoI difference < 10%.",
      "rationale": "E/uval was computed for all three QoIs across all 11 specimens. Maximum E/uval was 1.61 (force at 40 mm displacement). All QoI differences were below 10%. The ensemble of three FEA groups produced consistent predictions, with inter-model spread within experimental uncertainty bounds."
    },
    {
